\v 32 Mibuso yomhlaba, hlabelelani kuNkulunkulu, lihlabelele indumiso eNkosini. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 102.22.\x*.
\v 33 Kuyo egade\x + Dute. 33.26.\x* phezu kwamazulu amazulu awendulo\x + Dute. 10.14.\x*; khangelani, iphumisa ilizwi layo, ilizwi elilamandla\x + Hlab. 29.4.\x*.
\v 34 Phanini amandla kuNkulunkulu; ubukhosi bakhe buphezu kukaIsrayeli\x + Hlab. 29.1. Jobe 1.22.\x*, lamandla akhe\x + Hlab. 150.1.\x* asemayezini\x + Hlab. 36.5. 57.10. 78.23. 108.4.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Uyesabeka, Nkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 47.2. Hlab. 45.4. 65.5.\x*, ezindaweni zakho ezingcwele\x + Hlab. 110.2. 114.2.\x*; uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli nguye onika abantu \add bakhe\add* amandla lengalo. Kabongwe uNkulunkulu.